{
  "stem": "16163.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of-- most of us had short hair anyway, because of lice and et cetera in the beginning there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they cleaned the street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a-- what did they call it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were people who had to clean the streets up and fixed up some of the buildings from the outside.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just for the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they had a-- a ghetto music.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a ghetto concert-- a-- a ghetto band play music.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I think, I believe at that time they had what they called a cafe house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made like-- people could sit outside in a park area, you know, in a plaza [BACKROUND NOISE] type of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this was like nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a joke.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was gone again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was gone, was the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right after the thing when the Red Cross came and did the filming, the transport started again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Eichmann came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw Eichmann many times in-- in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as soon Eichmann came, you knew there was a transport going, or more then that--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know how I remember him?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Short, not tall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A short man in uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I understand that his family lived at one time as missionaries in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And what happened is that he approached some of the people and spoke Hebrew to them, because he lived in Palestine as a child or as a young man.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was known for what he was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was-- knew when he came, there was something was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
